name: AMAAAD X
description:
* Both other versions of AMAAAD where edited on 07/11/20 based on a video that i recorded on 12/17/17 from the view of a hotel balcony in Sayulita, Nayarit, Mexico just after eating half acid on that moment and a complete one the night before, same as the girl the i was on a date with. 



+ Memories from colorful psychedelic hallucinations on the beach and mad, young love. +



"AMAAAD X" (Acid Morning After An Acid Date X) is based on another video from that morning that i edited on 07/04/20 - a week before "AcID MoRNING AfFTER An AcID DaTE" & "AMAAAD" - but this one was actually recorded by the girl i was dating so here you can see myself smiling under the same palm trees in the end. 






Hi! °<>°
